des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your GoDirect smart cameras and other smart devices. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our "AuraHome Control" app in the app market then register an account;
(2) Configure your devices in "AuraHome Control" app and customize your device's names; 
(3) Download the Amazon "Alexa" app from Android, iOS or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search "AuraHome Control" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable "AuraHome Control" skill, and you'll be navigated to "AuraHome Control" login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete the linking process;
(7) Now the setup is complete. You can now enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, show me the camera.”
“Alexa, show me the backyard camera.”
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
